        "type": "email",
        "html": "<p>Hey {first_name, \"there\"},</p><p>I hope you're having a good morning. It's sunny and warm here on the Sussex coast, which is making me feel <em>really</em> good for a Monday morning just after the clocks went forward‚Ä¶</p><p>If you <a href=\"__GHOST_URL__/\">click through today</a>, you'll be able to see my new, cleaner site design. What do you think?</p>"
